Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.16,0:02:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了 亲爱的 今天的普拉提杂志到了吗\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}See you later, babe. Have you got Pilates today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.84,0:02:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没呢 等邮差送过来\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}No, got to wait in for the postman.
