Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.24,0:02:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好 那我走了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Sounds great. Have a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.84,0:02:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道会是什么\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I wonder what it could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你好 是劳拉·格兰特吗 -是我\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}-Hello, are you Lara Grant? -Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.84,0:04:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Do you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想喝杯水吗\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Want a glass of water?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要喝杯水\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Do you want a glass of water?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.32,0:04:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,药的说明上写着你可能会头痛\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}The instructions said you might have a headache.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.88,0:04:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要 我要\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.68,0:05:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝吧\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Drink up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.08,0:05:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这是在哪里\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要问问题\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}No questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这是怎么回事 -你要干嘛\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}-Please, what is this about? -What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Stop...talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.84,0:05:39.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 \N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听过你的声音了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}but I've already heard your voice, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你没必要用变声器的\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}You don't have to use that toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.16,0:05:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 也对\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.48,0:05:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还看过你的脸\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}And I've seen your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.28,0:05:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邮递员送信时是不戴面具的 对吧\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Well, I couldn't wear a mask as a postman, could I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样会吓到你的\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}You know, I might've scared you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.22,0:05:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 另外药品说明书上说\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Well, besides, the instructions said
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:06:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可能因为二氯甲烷而失忆\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}you might have memory loss from the dichloromethane.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下可怎么办才好\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Well, I don't know what to do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.64,0:06:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 你的样子我记不太清了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Well, I...I don't recall your features, if that's any help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只记得有个圆斑\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I just remember, like, a round blob.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-圆斑 -警方辨人的时候我也认不出你的\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}-Round blob? -I couldn't pick you out from a line-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 你到底是让我继续戴着面具\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Sorry, are you telling me to keep the mask on
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.24,0:06:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是摘了 我都糊涂了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}or to take it off? I'm confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.80,0:06:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都行 我不会跟任何人说的 我保证\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I don't mind, but I won't say anything to anybody, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.56,0:06:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我知道\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Oh, I know you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.84,0:06:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肯定不会让你说出去的\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I'll make sure of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.40,0:06:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你给我安静几分钟\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Now, you keep quiet for a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Ssh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.32,0:07:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳拉 我正忙着呢\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Lara, I'm really pushed for time at the moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长话短说好吗\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}so keep it quick, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.16,0:07:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多姆 快来救我 我被绑架了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Dom, listen, you've got to help me. I've been kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.72,0:07:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.88,0:07:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多姆 我被绑架了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Dom, I've been kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.24,0:07:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你大点儿声 \N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}You're gonna have to speak up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.12,0:07:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我听不见 -那个邮差绑架了我\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}-I can't hear you. -The postman kidnapped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.28,0:07:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰玛奇朵 至少来三杯\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Iced macchiato, at least three shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.48,0:07:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.64,0:08:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的 还是你吗\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Babe, is that you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么话快说 你想干嘛 我没那么多时间\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Well, come on, spit it out. What do you want? I'm short for time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.68,0:08:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老婆在我手上 我把她捆上了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I have your wife. She's tied up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.48,0:08:19.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳拉 别整什么电话调情了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Lara, you know I can't do phone sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这里可是开放式办公室\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I'm in an open-plan office.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你老婆在我手上\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I said I have your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.44,0:08:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.56,0:08:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细听好了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Listen very carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.80,0:08:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能别用那个蠢声音跟我说话了吗\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Will you stop putting on that stupid fucking voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-听着就让人上火 -你他妈给我听好了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}-It's really irritating... -Fucking listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.00,0:08:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁 你想干嘛\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Who is this? What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要你从\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}You need to make available
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.00,0:08:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,业务准备金账户提出130万英镑来\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}£1.3 million from your business reserve account
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后等下一步的命令\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}and await further instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.28,0:08:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话你老婆就死定了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Failure to do so will lead to the death of your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.36,0:08:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听明白了吗\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Is that clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呢 我才和我老婆通过话\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}What are you talking about? I just spoke to my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.82,0:08:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在家呢\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}She's at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.96,0:08:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-快点 -哼\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}-Come on. -Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在等一个包裹 对了 你是那个邮差吧\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}She's waiting in for a package. Oh, wait, are you the postman?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.54,0:09:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-多姆 -是我 你到底在哪里\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}-Dom! -Yeah, where exactly are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.14,0:09:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚接到个很奇怪的电话\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Cos I just had a very strange call from someone
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:18.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人说你被绑架了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}saying you've been kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.92,0:09:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 我就是想告诉你这个\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Yes! That's what I was trying to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.52,0:09:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得照他们说的去做 救我\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}You've got to do exactly what they say... Please! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.20,0:09:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳拉\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Lara?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.44,0:09:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不该这么干的\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}You shouldn't have done that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.48,0:09:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在几点了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.28,0:10:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11点半了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Half past 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.84,0:10:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经在这里三个小时了吗\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}So we've been here three hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.60,0:10:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是你家吗\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Is this your actual house?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}It is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.64,0:10:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不是吗\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然不是\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Oh, definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.32,0:10:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}So that's a yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.16,0:10:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.32,0:10:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 混蛋 你耍我\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Oh, bollocks. You tricked me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.68,0:10:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Y...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.72,0:10:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好吧 我来问你\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}All right, then, let me do you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你是叫劳拉吗 -是的\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}-Is your name Lara? -That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.68,0:10:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你老公有钱吗 -有钱\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}-Is your husband rich? -He is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他爱你吗 -我觉得是\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}-Does he love you? -I believe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.68,0:10:53.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他爱你胜过爱钱吗\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Does he love you more than he loves money?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:56.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就得等着瞧了 对吧\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Well, we'll see, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.32,0:11:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么把面具摘了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Why aren't you wearing your mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不该来这里的 怎么了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}You're not meant to be here. What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我都来了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I'm here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.72,0:11:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不打算让我进去吗\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Are you gonna let me in or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.08,0:11:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Yes.
