Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.24,0:18:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能问一下 你现在究竟想达到什么目的\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Can I just ask what exactly you're trying to achieve at this point?
